General.Name: Fiducian Group Ltd
General.Description: Fiducian Group Ltd, through its subsidiaries, provides financial services in Australia. It operates through Funds Management, Financial Planning, Corporate Services, and Platform Administration segments. The company provides investor directed portfolio and separately managed accounts services; and acts as the trustee of fiducial superannuation services. It also offers fiducial funds; financial planning services; client account administration platforms; and wrap platform administration services. In addition, the company develops IT software systems for financial planning; and offers financial advisory services, such as cash flow management, debt reduction, planning retirement, estate management, and aged care, as well as provides platform solutions and SMSF administration services. Further, it offers diversified and sector funds, specialist funds, managed portfolios, and manager system services. The company was founded in 1996 and is based in Sydney, Australia.
